            <span class="brand semibold"> Read the full story </span>
          </mj-button>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section mj-class="preSection">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="p">If you're enjoying the tips following on <a class="underA" href="https://twitter.com/GoodMarketingHQ" target="_blank">twitter</a> keeps me motivated. Building out a community forum atm :)</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="p">Cheers, <br>Harry</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="p">p.s. - to get in touch just reply to this email :)</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
